title: Rochard's no-hitter leads No. 5 Virginia Tech over No. 22/20UCF 1-0 - VT hokiesports.com
content: Rochard's no-hitter leads No. 5 Virginia Tech over No. 22/20UCF 1-0  VT hokiesports.com
description: ORLANDO, Fla. -- Senior Keely Rochard turned in a great performance on Sunday, tossing a no-hitter and striking out 14 to lead the No. 5 Virginia Tech Hokies past the No. 22/20 UCF Knights 1-0. This is Rochard's eighth career no-hitter and her first of the season.
